27
00:03:45.909 --> 00:03:48.247
Sean. we need to
pull together now.

28
00:03:48.347 --> 00:03:50.126
- If Elliot phones. don't answer.
- What?

29
00:03:50.226 --> 00:03:52.364
You're not doing what
he says. He'll kill...

30
