41
00:04:42.072 --> 00:04:46.310
I never want to see you. or
speak to you. ever again.

42
00:04:47.509 --> 00:04:49.507
Do you understand?

43
00:04:50.907 --> 00:04:53.225
Your father would
have finished the job.

44
00:05:00.580 --> 00:05:03.219
